snippet.title: Mineko's Night Market - Meet the Town Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Mineko’s Night Market is a game that celebrates Japanese culture while introducing a heartwarming story about friendship, tradition, and many, many cats. In this all new trailer, explore Mineko's new home and get to know her new neighbors.

Mineko’s Night Market is coming soon to Nintendo Switch. Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/minekos-night-market-switch/
